Class StackMarkerObj

  • java.lang.Object
    • Argument
      • StackMarkerObj
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.Comparator

    public class StackMarkerObj
extends Argument
    This class provides a marker that can be inserted into a stack of Arguments. It is used in the 'expand' methods to keep track of the number of levels of recursion that have already been expanded.
